sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant AuthProxy as kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Head as Ray Head Pod
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant ServeSvc as Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation & Dashboard Access (OpenShift/RHOAI)

        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayCluster created)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create head pod, worker pods,<br/>services, RBAC, NetworkPolicies<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>CertMgr: Create Issuer + Certificates<br/>(mTLS: CA 10yr, node 90d)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant,<br/>auth proxy secrets
        Note over Operator: Authentication Controller creates<br/>HTTPRoute in platform namespace

        User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/<br/>Auth: Session cookie
        Gateway->>AuthProxy: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed TLS)<br/>Auth: SubjectAccessReview
        AuthProxy->>Dashboard: Proxy to localhost<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (loopback, no auth)
        Dashboard-->>AuthProxy: Dashboard HTML response
        AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: Dashboard UI
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,Workers: Flow 2: RayJob Submission (HTTP Mode)

        Operator->>Dashboard: POST /api/jobs/<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (cluster-internal, no auth)
        Dashboard->>Head: Schedule job execution
        Head->>Workers: Distribute tasks<br/>gRPC (mTLS if enabled)
        Workers-->>Head: Task results
        Operator->>Dashboard: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>Poll status (cluster-internal)
        Dashboard-->>Operator: Job status (SUCCEEDED/FAILED)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Operator,ServeSvc: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Upgrade (Blue-Green)

        Operator->>Dashboard: PUT /api/serve/applications/<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (pending cluster)
        Note over Operator: Push Serve config to pending cluster
        Operator->>ServeSvc: GET /health (HTTP proxy)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        Note over Operator: Monitor application health
        ServeSvc-->>Operator: Health status (HEALTHY)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Service selector<br/>(switch active → pending)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Note over Operator: Atomic traffic cutover<br/>Old cluster deleted after switch
    end
